# Agent Rules

## Workflow

- Read only files relevant to the task.
- Avoid scanning the entire project.
- Search before opening files.
- Keep context minimal.

## Coding

- Modify existing code whenever possible.
- Create new files only when necessary.
- Follow existing project patterns.
- Keep implementations simple.

## Output

- Give concise explanations.
- Show only relevant code.
- Avoid repeating information.

## Planning

- For large tasks create a short plan.
- Execute step by step.
- Re-evaluate after each completed step.

## Token Efficiency

- Do not reread files already understood.
- Do not summarize large files unless requested.
- Avoid loading unrelated directories.